# OWM-Dataset

## Description
The dataset contains processed intracranial EEG recordings from frontal and temporal areas of patients performing an object working memory task.

## Trial retrieval
To comply with the .edf format, processed trials (6499 ms each) for every channel were concatenated to a single one-dimensional array. Due to a different number of valid trials across channels, each such array was then padded with 0s on the right ensuring the same data length for all channels within a subject. The total number of concatenated trials per channel and the padding length are recorded in the "_channels.tsv" file for each subject.